Package biz.gabrys.lesscss.compiler2

Class FileSystemOption

  • java.lang.Object
    • biz.gabrys.lesscss.compiler2.FileSystemOption
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    public class FileSystemOption
extends Object
implements Serializable

    Represents --file-system option. The option should be defined in the following format: classname(,parameterslist) where:

    • classname - java class name (example org.example.FileSystem)
    • parameterslist - comma separated list of parameters (example: param1=value1,param2=value2)

    Special characters used in parameters names or values have to be escaped in parameters list by adding underscore character before:

    • underscore "_" -> two underscores "__"
    • comma "," -> underscore + comma "_,"
    • equal "=" -> underscore + equal "_="
    Since:
    2.0.0
    See Also:
    FileSystem, FileSystemOptionBuilder, Serialized Form
